## Additional Notes on Assets

### Visual Content
Visual assets (images, icons, emoji) used in this project are for **demonstration and personal use only**. These may include:
- API-generated content
- Free-to-use asset libraries
- Custom-created visual elements

**Important:** Please do not redistribute visual assets commercially without proper licensing verification.

### Kanji & Typography
Japanese kanji characters (幸福, 悲しみ, etc.) are used for aesthetic and cultural expression purposes. These are part of standard Unicode character sets and are used respectfully within the context of emotional representation.

### Audio
Sound effects are generated programmatically using the Web Audio API and are original to this project.
